NỘI DUNG CHÍNH
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  • Truy cập Handbook
      • linuxfoundation.org → Handbook cho online exams

  • Candidate Requirements
      • Video demo trải nghiệm thi
      • System requirements: Browser, OS, one monitor

  • Exam Registration
      • Fees theo khu vực
      • Certification catalog
      • Checkout & payment
      • Linux Foundation account

  • During Exam
      • Quiet, well-lit room, no other people/equipment
      • No phone/smartwatch
      • Timer, instructions, remote desktop
      • End Exam button

  • After Exam
      • Results trong 24 giờ
      • Score ≥66% để pass
      • Certification valid 36 months

  • Preparation Checklist
      • Verify system, schedule/reschedule

  • Key Takeaways
      • Handbook là tài liệu quan trọng
      • Practice lab, understand rules


